      "relations": null,
      "text": [
        " قَالَ أَبُو جَعْفَرٍ ( عليه السلام ) إِنَّ أَشَدَّ الْعِبَادَةِ الْوَرَعُ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "From him, from his father, from Fazalat Bin Ayoub, from Al Hassan Bin Ziyad Al Sayqal, from Fuzayl Bin Yasaar who said, ",
          "‘Abu Ja’far<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘The most difficult of the worship is the devoutness’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "5. It is narrated from him (narrator of the Hadith above) from his father from Fadalah ibn Ayyub from al-Hassan ibn Ziyad al-Sayqal from Fudayl ibn Yasar from abu Ja’far who has said the following: “Abu Ja’far (a.s.) has said, ‘Restraining from worldly matters (sins) is the most intense form of worship.’” "
        ]
      }
